Package: sway-mirror
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Fast zero-copy screen mirroring for Sway/wlroots
 A high-performance screen mirroring tool for Sway and other
 wlroots-based Wayland compositors. Features include:
  - Zero-copy buffer sharing via DMA-BUF
  - Low latency mirroring
  - Multiple scaling modes (fit, fill, stretch, center)
  - Cursor mirroring support
